OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA mostly dry
OL,6,Fevening and night with plenty of clear
OL,7,Fspells. Some low cloud developing over
OL,8,Fthe hills in the far west during the
OL,9,Fearly hours. Staying mild.
OL,10,
OL,11,CFriday:FTurning cloudier this morning
OL,12,Fwith a few spots of rain likely,
OL,13,Fbefore clearing eastwards. Skies
OL,14,Fbrightening by the afternoon, with
OL,15,Fplenty of sunshine developing.
OL,16,FGenerally feeling fresher than of late.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
