OL,5,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FA
OL,6,Fbright start to Saturday, but heavy
OL,7,Frain moving in later on in the day.
OL,8,FSunshine and showers for Sunday and
OL,9,Fthen potentially wetter and winder on
OL,10,FMonday. Feeling cooler.
